<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>CookMeThis - Blog</title>
    @vite(['resources/css/app.css'])
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        {{-- <img src="/resources/views/pages/banner.jpg" alt="CookMeThis Banner" class="banner"> --}}
        <h1>CookMeThis</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/search">Recipes</a></li>
                <li><a href="/popular">Popular</a></li>
                <li><a href="/blog">Blog</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <h1>Featured Recipes</h1>
            <div class="recipe-container">
                @each(recipe in recipes)
                <article class="recipe-card">
                    <img src="{{ recipe.image }}" alt="{{ recipe.title }}">
                    <h3>{{ recipe.title }}</h3>
                    <p>{{{ recipe.instructions }}}</p>
                </article>
                @endeach
            </div>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h1>Latest Posts</h1>
            <div class="blog-posts">
                <article class="blog-post">
                    <h3>10 Tips for Perfect Pasta</h3>
                    <p>Discover the secrets to making the perfect pasta with our top 10 tips. From selecting the right
                        ingredients to cooking techniques, learn how to elevate your pasta dishes.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="blog-post">
                    <h3>How to Bake the Best Chocolate Chip Cookies</h3>
                    <p>Get ready to bake the best chocolate chip cookies ever. Follow our step-by-step guide and enjoy
                        delicious, gooey cookies that are sure to be a hit with everyone.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="blog-post">
                    <h3>The Health Benefits of a Mediterranean Diet</h3>
                    <p>Explore the numerous health benefits of the Mediterranean diet. Learn how incorporating fresh,
                        wholesome ingredients into your meals can improve your overall well-being.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>

</html>